Dear Renato,

I've never used this package and you did not attached a reproducible 
example, so I cannot test my suggestion. Nevertheless, please try 
converting the column "i" to factor before calling the t2way() and 
mcp2atm() functions, and replace "as.factor(i)" with "i" in the model 
formulas:
khg$i <- as.factor(khg$i)
t2way(formula = fr ~ t * i, data = khg)
mcp2atm(fr ~ t * i, data = khg)
Since you read the khg.txt file with stringsAsFactors = TRUE 
parameterization, the factor conversion can be skipped if "i" contained 
text. If it contained numbers, then the conversion is needed.

HTH,
?kos
